The Word Game: "Decrypto" in the Game Test
The players form two teams that sit opposite each other.
For each page there is a screen, in it four cards with keywords, which you can only decipher - the old trick with the red foil - once you have put them in.
This ensures that the other side cannot read anything even by mistake.
On the cards, for example, it says from left to right: "1st Renaissance.
2. Windows.
